{"tid":1238294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HA事件集中討論區","createTime":"2019-06-17T18:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T18:48:05.000Z","uid":39777,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9f57c2872ff2a2d594f76c64d6f5482d5af2d841","tid":1238294,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:19:36.000Z","msg":"首先我想從陳沛然議員的blog的發文，同陳沛然議員係youtube曾經上載過既影片進行交叉對照同分析<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gvUxKcj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgvUxKcj.png&h=79845999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XfR4AiZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXfR4AiZ.jpg&h=e2572c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一欄其實好易明，報左係立法會大型示威入黎既傷者。<br />\n有可以睇到既有HKID，性別，姓名，年齡，Condition(穩定、嚴重、危殆之類)<br />\n入出院時間同埋依家留係醫院邊一個地方(location)<br />\n<br />\n但第二欄目就引起我一D思考，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(A)Pneumonia</span></span></strong><br />\nGoogle過係肺炎咁解。我原先認為所有人都應該係吸引催淚煙引發肺炎然後求醫<br />\n可能因為無報過去過立會，所以入資料時只有按病徵歸類為Pneumonia<br />\n但我仔細思考下呢個假設存在不合理既地方，示威者帶去一個兩歲三歲既BB，BB食左催淚煙，然後決定於6月13號下午先求醫？很難想像<br />\n<br />\n所以更合理既假設我認為係呢引list除左會gen左入左disaster code既傷者/病人。亦都會用一些篩選條件(例如12-13號因為肺炎入院求醫)既清單，再按年齡(因主要感染肺炎既人多為初生嬰兒or年老人士)搵出一D目標，例如俾著係我會留意一位30歲同36歲女士因肺炎入院<br />\n<br />\n最後，我既結論or總結係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢一張清單，係有極其針對性同目的性去嘗試搵出有去過既示威者出黎。即使示威者避開無提供過去過邊到，醫護入資料時無擺入disaster code入面。仍然透過篩選條件(肺炎)去鎖定示威者</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nPS以上係我假設同我既推理，歡迎討論"},{"pid":"b558f31c2adbdf375cd71b699318b723e3e519a6","tid":1238294,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:19:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5bc257cc94dad5a7f6d9683455338eaf2c759f5","tid":1238294,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:20:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"662f8ffead7c97241564bd0a89ac02e95e6c657f","tid":1238294,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:20:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"697753bbac32231e949771d20ed5ae078e419f30","tid":1238294,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:24:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39847fedb51785bea39fe275d68bd743bf5e0f71","tid":1238294,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:28:23.000Z","msg":"真係要俾人知"},{"pid":"dc5bb1f408ced1f68fab16dc9cf31ecea5d67e0e","tid":1238294,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:31:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d886a75d01c1400cf59a7a6474a08de88579ef26","tid":1238294,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:31:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"576c80cc32af04ca8b0cbf1733e73715fbbec3e9","tid":1238294,"uid":100714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:33:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9547214729a7a407f7dd168be7e0213452e289f","tid":1238294,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:33:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e7294a1a54c36f9b088e85fb083bf75bf396163","tid":1238294,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:34:34.000Z","msg":"會唔會condom仔入左急症check"},{"pid":"03668fce857cb42ee0a1a4ee008a8e21983496f8","tid":1238294,"uid":96248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:34:50.000Z","msg":"應該係第一個list太短 所以順住出落去"},{"pid":"670540320a0cdc62bb9beb97ce904a76e14df45b","tid":1238294,"uid":39777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03668fce857cb42ee0a1a4ee008a8e21983496f8","tid":1238294,"uid":96248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:34:50.000Z","msg":"應該係第一個list太短 所以順住出落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:37:04.000Z","msg":"但真係會有人帶2歲BB去612示威，食左催淚凐，隔日先去求醫？"},{"pid":"2602c2e57ce8ea8e48f1ca6aae5424bf15a1e392","tid":1238294,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl